826
01:30:24,539 --> 01:30:25,455
Careful.

827
01:30:43,705 --> 01:30:46,080
Let's go..

828
01:30:47,914 --> 01:30:49,455
Armin, let's go!

829
01:30:53,955 --> 01:30:56,447
<i>Armin, you quickly pack your stuff,
I will meet you in 10 minutes!</i>

