01:52:32,962 --> 01:52:35,128
<i>.. I don't know how I..?</i>

1099
01:52:37,471 --> 01:52:41,545
<i>When you did not recognize
me in the hospital..</i>

1100
01:52:42,923 --> 01:52:47,420
