1101
01:52:47,503 --> 01:52:50,295
<i>I understood that you
didn't remember anything..</i>

1102
01:52:50,545 --> 01:52:54,337
<i>And then you said your name as Armin.</i>

1103
01:52:54,586 --> 01:53:00,212
<i>I understood that you had
